PdV python scripts - README file
================================


PURPOSE
-------

This is a bunch of python scripts + OpenFrameworks used for the theater show PdV (http://rogerbernat.info) .
The show needs a voting system (hadware) and a voting analysis & visualization system (software: python + OpenFrameworks).


